title: Human Events Daily - Sep 27 2021 - Anti-Mandate Activists In New York City
description:
Check out what anti-mandate activists in New York City did to speak out against draconian segregation in their city, the Biden administration is turning on itself starting with VP Kamala Harris, military members that are about to be kicked out for refusing the vaccine take to TikTok, and hear what this CNN guest had to say about Speaker Pelosi’s $3.5T spending bill.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
